  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vanquish thousands of enemies in this class-based action roguelite. Collect experience, level-up, and evolve your weapons to gain overwhelming power. Complete quests to unlock persistent bonuses and weapon modifiers for your next run. Will you conquer or become just another forgotten casualty?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight off hordes of thousands of enemies and the unique bosses that lead them, in action-packed 20 minute runs.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/cb86a06c64f8d8cf95fd4aaf2bfd9a2f.poster.avif?t=1731535117\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/cb86a06c64f8d8cf95fd4aaf2bfd9a2f.webm?t=1731535117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/cb86a06c64f8d8cf95fd4aaf2bfd9a2f.mp4?t=1731535117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your class, each with their own unique weapons and playstyles. Unleash powerful attacks as the Warrior, teleport and dodge enemies as the Rogue, and inflict elemental conditions as the Mage.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/4652955a452d235cc0db4500d8b49431.poster.avif?t=1731535117\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/4652955a452d235cc0db4500d8b49431.webm?t=1731535117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/4652955a452d235cc0db4500d8b49431.mp4?t=1731535117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evolve weapons into new, powerful forms to unleash devastating power.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/b04d9652e87cc49305dea415b64d6606.poster.avif?t=1731535117\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/b04d9652e87cc49305dea415b64d6606.webm?t=1731535117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/b04d9652e87cc49305dea415b64d6606.mp4?t=1731535117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Power-up between runs. Increase your stats with Boons, customize your weapons in the Armory, and rescue Orcphans to improve your luck.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/f788e8290f4cc11010bd3a0d141fa8bb.poster.avif?t=1731535117\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/f788e8290f4cc11010bd3a0d141fa8bb.webm?t=1731535117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/f788e8290f4cc11010bd3a0d141fa8bb.mp4?t=1731535117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local co-op for up to 3 players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 unique weapons per class, each with 15+ weapon modifiers to unlock and apply.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prove your skills across 10 levels of difficulty. Higher difficulty levels increase the strength of enemies, changes their spawn patterns, and introduces empowered champions and bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete hundreds of quests and collect dozens of cosmetic hats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Track your progress with the Compendium and uncover the secrets of the world of Orc Survivor. </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vanquish thousands of enemies in this class-based action roguelite. Collect experience, level-up, and evolve your weapons to gain overwhelming power. Complete quests to unlock persistent bonuses and weapon modifiers for your next run. Will you conquer or become just another forgotten casualty?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight off hordes of thousands of enemies and the unique bosses that lead them, in action-packed 20 minute runs.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/cb86a06c64f8d8cf95fd4aaf2bfd9a2f.poster.avif?t=1731535117\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/cb86a06c64f8d8cf95fd4aaf2bfd9a2f.webm?t=1731535117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/cb86a06c64f8d8cf95fd4aaf2bfd9a2f.mp4?t=1731535117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your class, each with their own unique weapons and playstyles. Unleash powerful attacks as the Warrior, teleport and dodge enemies as the Rogue, and inflict elemental conditions as the Mage.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/4652955a452d235cc0db4500d8b49431.poster.avif?t=1731535117\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/4652955a452d235cc0db4500d8b49431.webm?t=1731535117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/4652955a452d235cc0db4500d8b49431.mp4?t=1731535117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evolve weapons into new, powerful forms to unleash devastating power.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/b04d9652e87cc49305dea415b64d6606.poster.avif?t=1731535117\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/b04d9652e87cc49305dea415b64d6606.webm?t=1731535117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/b04d9652e87cc49305dea415b64d6606.mp4?t=1731535117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Power-up between runs. Increase your stats with Boons, customize your weapons in the Armory, and rescue Orcphans to improve your luck.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/f788e8290f4cc11010bd3a0d141fa8bb.poster.avif?t=1731535117\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/f788e8290f4cc11010bd3a0d141fa8bb.webm?t=1731535117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643960/extras/f788e8290f4cc11010bd3a0d141fa8bb.mp4?t=1731535117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local co-op for up to 3 players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 unique weapons per class, each with 15+ weapon modifiers to unlock and apply.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prove your skills across 10 levels of difficulty. Higher difficulty levels increase the strength of enemies, changes their spawn patterns, and introduces empowered champions and bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete hundreds of quests and collect dozens of cosmetic hats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Track your progress with the Compendium and uncover the secrets of the world of Orc Survivor. </p></li></ul>",
